HEADWORD: Feræ naturæ
<hw>Fe"r⟦ae⟧ na*tu"r⟦ae⟧</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[L.]</ety> <def>Of a wild nature; -- applied to animals, as foxes, wild ducks, etc., in which no one can claim property.</def>⟦br⟧
